@context: E-commerce purchase flow on SauceDemo
@blueprint: swag-labs-checkout

1. NAVIGATE to https://www.saucedemo.com/
2. Fill 'Username' with 'standard_user'
3. Fill 'Password' with 'secret_sauce'
4. Click 'Login' button
5. VERIFY that 'Products' is present
6. Click 'Add to cart' near 'Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket'
7. NAVIGATE to https://www.saucedemo.com/cart.html
8. VERIFY that 'Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket' is present
9. Click 'Checkout' button
10. Fill 'First Name' with 'FirstName'
11. Fill 'Last Name' with 'LastName'
12. Fill 'Zip/Postal Code' with '49000'
13. Click 'Continue' button
14. Click 'Finish' button
15. VERIFY that 'Thank you for your order!' is present
16. DONE.